entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found information about an Imperial project to develope a new, volatile energy source.
entries.journal_entry_description: An Ithorian scientist has information about an Imperial project underway on Corellia.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Just outside of an Imperial warehouse, meet with an Ithorian scientist, T'licl Zanedi, who has information on what the Empire is up to in that warehouse.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Empire is developing a new energy source of some sort. Find out what you can about this project.
entries.task01_task_display_string_3: Recover a Sample of the Compound
entries.task03_item_name: You have a sample of the compound
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: According to T'licl, a compound that has been developed is one of the keystones of this Imperial project. Find a sample of that compound.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Recover a Sample of the Compound
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find some development notes about the energy source project that detail what the empire has done thus far.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Get the design overview of the project. That should reveal more about what the Empire is planning to do with an energy source of this kind.
